Package cz.cuni.mff.java.klima.pacman.map

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.java.klima.pacman.map.Map
  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    The Map class is the class responsible for controlling all the game characters by calling their tick and render methods.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Map

        public Map​(Handler handler,
           int level)
        Constructor of the Map class. It takes the game handler, for having access to all elements of the game, and level number as parameters. It calls the loadMap method to load the game map of the correct level.
        Parameters:
        handler - game handler for accessing other elements of the game
        level - current game level (map to be loaded)
